              "type": "text",
              "text": {
                "content": "Collaborative learning benefits from clustering students into appropriate learner groups. However, most group optimization is performed via single-objective optimization, not accounting for multiple constraints. To address this, authors propose a multi-objective Genetic algorithm, NSGA-II. ",
                "link": null
              },
              "annotations": {
