              "plain_text": "Collaborative learning benefits from clustering students into appropriate learner groups. However, most group optimization is performed via single-objective optimization, not accounting for multiple constraints. To address this, authors propose a multi-objective Genetic algorithm, NSGA-II. ",
              "href": null
